HIBERNATE
---------


UUID:
    1. Entity with relations: ASSIGN A NULL TO ALL UUIDs BY DEFAULT, so that they can be automatically generated
     in the relationships at the time of insertions in the database !!! And use JoinColumn, dont PKJoinColumn
    . Only entity: Use @GeneratedValue (AUTO is default) y dont use IDENTITY to avoid getting the following error:
        org.hibernate.id.IdentifierGenerationException: unrecognized id type : pg-uuid -> java.util.UUID

    Sources:
        1. https://stackoverflow.com/a/64096963/5279996
        https://stackoverflow.com/a/64057902/5279996

